    "Furthermore, AI can also be integrated into metasurfaces themselves, enabling all-optical machine learning and accelerating computational tasks.",
    "These advancements open up new opportunities for metasurfaces in diverse fields, including imaging, communication, sensing, and computing.",
    "Conclusions and outlooksMetasurface and AI, as the cutting-edge research directions in the fields of optics and computer science in the 21st century, have demonstrated a strong trend of interdisciplinary integration.",
